{'geocode_type': 'EVDB Geocoder', 'event_count': '52', 'trackback_count': '0', 'comment_count': '4', 'region_abbr': 'PA', 'postal_code': '15209', 'latitude': '40.480855', 'url': 'http://pittsburgh.eventful.com/venues/mr-smalls-funhouse-theatre-/V0-001-001308361-3?utm_source=apis&utm_medium=apim&utm_campaign=apic', 'id': 'V0-001-001308361-3', 'address': '400 Lincoln Avenue', 'city_name': 'Pittsburgh', 'owner': 'spongebobandme87', 'link_count': '23', 'country_name': 'United States', 'longitude': '-79.972264', 'timezone': None, 'country_abbr': 'USA', 'region_name': 'Pennsylvania', 'country_abbr2': 'US', 'name': "Mr. Small's Funhouse & Theatre", 'description': '

Mr Smalls Funhouse is located just five minutes from downtown Pittsburgh.\nThe venue started out as one single recording studio, and has since grown to include a 650-capacity theatre, an art gallery, skate-park, Rock Hostel for Artist housing, and two full-service recording studios. Today, Mr Smalls stands as one of the premier live entertainment venues in Pittsburgh. Indeed, its signature feature, Mr Smalls Theatre, is widely considered to be among the best small music venues in the country.

The venue's reputation is evident when you look at the list of music stars who have performed, recorded or both at Mr Smalls in the past. Black Eyed Peas, 50 Cent, Ryan Adams, Gomez, Anti-Flag and KT Tunstall are just a few of those featured on the Mr Smalls schedule in the past.

So why not plan your visit today? Make Evenful your source for all the latest news and up-to-date events information from Mr Smalls Funhouse Pittsburgh, and check out the schedule right here!
